{"tid":938081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄戰略轟炸機降落委內瑞拉 激怒美國","createTime":"2018-12-12T04:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T11:40:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fac09294c7d3d395c75a7b4e29fe81058dd9264d","tid":938081,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"俄戰略轟炸機降落委內瑞拉 激怒美國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3531868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3531868&d=cGeTo8mfJM0e0XC%2FG8%2BgJ%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=065c8808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3531868</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯兩架可攜帶核武的戰略轟炸機降落在盟邦委內瑞拉，以展現對委國政府的支持，但激怒了美國。<br />\n<br />\n俄國飛行員暱稱為「白天鵝」（White Swans）的TU－160超音速轟炸機飛過了1萬多公里航程，今天降落在委國首都卡拉卡斯附近的邁格狄亞（Maiquetia）機場。<br />\n<br />\n數天前，委內瑞拉總統馬杜洛（Nicolas Maduro）曾在莫斯科與俄國總統蒲亭（Vladimir Putin）會談。委內瑞拉左翼政府是美國在拉丁美洲的大敵。<br />\n<br />\n可攜帶短程核子飛彈的TU－160轟炸機，無須空中加油即可持續飛行1.2萬公里以上。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）在推特發文怒斥：「俄國政府派轟炸機飛越半個地球到委內瑞拉。」<br />\n<br />\n「俄國和委內瑞拉民眾應該看穿事情的真相，即在兩國人民受苦的情況下，這兩個貪腐政府依然浪費公帑，並打壓自由。」"},{"pid":"f8a2a408f976994c09eb852c7bb367a8736c2518","tid":938081,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉仲未滅國咩？應該都起碼死左10分1人了掛"},{"pid":"2976585929eee4bc3148738853cbdf8516a9276f","tid":938081,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"tu 160<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8db6bab333205276e3d1ac8e5d33ea9faf2f80","tid":938081,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"近來日本好多特別音樂訊號<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WCDY2gm0NH0&amp;index=10&amp;list=PLhNTQNc39PRQxycK3a7